data.description: This sprawling brick ranch is in the perfect location! Minutes away from shopping, schools, and Cherokee Golf course. This 4 bedroom, 3 full bath home gives every family member plenty of space.  Formal dining and living room as well as a den and sitting room off of the renovated kitchen. Such a stunner! Backyard is secluded and perfect for the kiddos to play outside all summer long. Patio overlooks spacious back yard and has ample room for all of your grilling and dining outdoors! You need to see this one!
